reviewText: I was dissapointed with this dvd for 2 reasons: 1 - it was a low budget dvd filmed in what seemed to be  an empty apartment living room. No special decor or music.  2 - the moves were so boring and basic, really a 6 year old or elderly person could do them. There was nothing unique or original about the moves. In the end, they were just beginner beginner bellydance motions. And when I say beginner beginner that is not a typo, as it is more basic than any beginner level video or class that I have tried in bellydancing, which makes it so monotonous. Save your money and watch a youtube vid for a bellydance intro class for free for the same results.
